    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Furniture designed by architects or to match or accord with the architectural features of the rooms for which it is intended.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
